    The LogicalInterconnectGroups data transfer object (DTO) contains the information used to represent LogicalInterconnectGroups in the system. The LogicalInterconnectGroups Dto is a generic specification of a set of uplink set that is used to channel the data(both vlan and fiber channel network) and the type of interconnect that is used in the virtual connect to aid in the purpose.It is passed in to the add/update logicalInterconnectGroups REST api, as well as the add/update logicalInterconnectGroups through java client api.
